title: InitializeBACnetDevObjPropReference (Function)
text:
FUNCTION InitializeBACnetDevObjPropReference : BOOL
Initializes a IEC_BACNET_DEV_OBJ_PROP_REFERENCE according to a given BACnetDevObjPropReference.

rows.Name: devObjPropRef
rows.Comment: The BACnetDevObjPropReference to use for initialization.

rows.Name: bacDevObjPropRef
rows.Comment: The BACnet device object property reference to operate on.
